OL,3,CPolice investigating deaths of 13
OL,4,Clambs with 'deliberately broken' necks
OL,6,FA farmer has spoken to UTV about his
OL,7,F'complete horror' after he discovered
OL,8,Fthat 13 of his lambs had their necks
OL,9,Fdeliberately broken.
OL,11,FPolice launched an investigation after
OL,12,Fthe animals were found dead at a farm
OL,13,Fon the Drumsesk Road in Rostrevor on
OL,14,FSaturday morning.
OL,16,FAn police inspector said it appeared
OL,17,Ftheir necks had been "deliberately
OL,18,Fbroken", calling it a "shocking crime"
OL,19,Fas he appealed for witnesses.
OL,26,@yD@VOUzD@GO]zD@WOUzD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
