OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1773688273
OL,3,CPolice investigating deaths of 13
OL,4,Clambs with 'deliberately broken' necks
OL,6,FSpeaking to UTV, farmer and owner of
OL,7,Fthe lambs Kevin McGivern said:
OL,8,F"Yesterday morning, me and the brother
OL,9,Fcame here as usual between half-seven
OL,10,Fand eight, to look at the sheep.
OL,12,F"And I just noticed from this point
OL,13,Fhere, looked up the field, and when I
OL,14,Fwent up the field, there was 13 lambs
OL,15,Flying very close together. Some of
OL,16,Fthem was actually nose-to-tail on
OL,17,Fthe`on the`on the ground. And most had
OL,18,Ftheir necks broken."
OL,20,FFor Kevin, the loss is not only
OL,21,Ffinancial but deeply distressing.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1773688273
OL,3,CPolice investigating deaths of 13
OL,4,Clambs with 'deliberately broken' necks
OL,6,FHe continued: "Cruelty to the lambs,
OL,7,Flike... we spent the year trying to
OL,8,Fget to this point of lambing.
OL,10,F"That's what it's all about, and it's
OL,11,Fbeen a very severe winter. Me and the
OL,12,Fbrother suffered a lot to get the
OL,13,Fsheep this far. And to see this end
OL,14,Fresult is not nice.
OL,16,F"Especially so close to good weather
OL,17,Fnow, when these lambs in a few weeks'
OL,18,Ftime would be skipping and playing
OL,19,Faround the field. Now they're lying up
OL,20,Fon the hill up there."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1773688273
OL,3,CPolice investigating deaths of 13
OL,4,Clambs with 'deliberately broken' necks
OL,6,FSpeaking on the tradgedy Independent
OL,7,FCllr Jarlath Tinnelly said:
OL,8,F"Absolutely reprehensible what has
OL,9,Fhappened here.
OL,11,F"And I'm sure that was a very
OL,12,Fharrowing experience for them when
OL,13,Fthey came on the scene here yesterday
OL,14,Fmorning.
OL,16,F"So my heart really does go out to
OL,17,Fthem, that them men are spending their
OL,18,FSunday afternoon up there gathering up
OL,19,Fdead lambs that are only a matter of
OL,20,Fweeks old."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
