CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1773688273
OL,3,CPolice investigating deaths of 13
OL,4,Clambs with 'deliberately broken' necks
OL,6,FIn a statement police said: "We
OL,7,Freceived a report that the lambs had
OL,8,Fbeen killed at a farm on Drumsesk Road
OL,9,Fat some point between 7pm on Friday
OL,10,FMarch 13 and 7.45am on Saturday March
OL,11,F14," the inspector said.
OL,13,F"It appears that their necks had been
OL,14,Fdeliberately broken.
OL,16,F"This is a shocking crime, and we
OL,17,Fwould be keen to hear from anyone who
OL,18,Fnoticed anything unusual in the area
OL,19,Fduring the times above.
OL,26,@nD@]OUsD@DO]uD@AOUxD@AOU
